## 🔎 Static Analysis - What to Look For

```bash
# Find hardcoded secrets
grep -r "password\|secret\|api_key\|token\|key=" output_dir/
grep -r "AWS\|firebase\|google" output_dir/
grep -r "http://\|https://" output_dir/   # API endpoints

# Check AndroidManifest.xml
cat output_dir/AndroidManifest.xml

# Look for:
# - android:debuggable="true"
# - android:allowBackup="true"  
# - exported components (android:exported="true")
# - custom permissions
# - intent filters

# Find SQLite databases in decompiled code
grep -r "SQLiteDatabase\|openDatabase\|execSQL" output_dir/

# Find webview usage
grep -r "WebView\|setJavaScriptEnabled\|addJavascriptInterface" output_dir/

# Find crypto usage
grep -r "AES\|DES\|MD5\|SHA1\|SecretKeySpec" output_dir/

# Find logging (may leak sensitive data)
grep -r "Log.d\|Log.e\|Log.v\|System.out.print" output_dir/
```

