## 📱 Dynamic Analysis with ADB

```bash
# Connect device
adb devices
adb connect 192.168.1.x:5555   # wireless

# Install APK
adb install target.apk

# Shell access
adb shell

# Pull files from device
adb pull /data/data/com.target.app/ ./app_data/

# Push files to device
adb push burp_cert.cer /sdcard/

# Logcat (real-time logs)
adb logcat | grep "com.target.app"
adb logcat -s "TAG_NAME"

# List installed apps
adb shell pm list packages | grep target

# Get APK path
adb shell pm path com.target.app

# Pull APK from device
adb pull /data/app/com.target.app-1/base.apk

# Launch activity
adb shell am start -n com.target.app/.MainActivity

# Send intent
adb shell am broadcast -a com.target.app.ACTION --es key value
```

