## 🗄️ Data Storage Security

```bash
# Check shared preferences (after adb shell)
ls /data/data/com.target.app/shared_prefs/
cat /data/data/com.target.app/shared_prefs/prefs.xml

# Check databases
ls /data/data/com.target.app/databases/
sqlite3 /data/data/com.target.app/databases/app.db
.tables
SELECT * FROM users;

# Check files directory
ls /data/data/com.target.app/files/

# Check external storage
ls /sdcard/Android/data/com.target.app/

# Check for world-readable files
find /data/data/com.target.app -perm -o+r
```

